  "description": "A cute Obsidian-Colored Dark Themed GUI Pack in the style of the Allure resource pack!",
  "body": "<center>\n<h1><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3a9c9b681858fef475b9b6b240c57b280a34bcfc.png\" alt=\"Allure micropacks\"></h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-3d-plants/\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8a2dd1324a19f7594a6e032659b78fb3e5e89a2d.png\" alt=\"Modrinth\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/allure-6439754/\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/48f3ed3f11e619ef7fea93c4344ae8f4ba233cb0.png\" alt=\"Planet Minecraft\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/p4ncake\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/1fab8f2e1518ab9f6373586085d9aa785e0e3b9d.png\" alt=\"Support me on Ko-Fi\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/C9Q6XFG8T8\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6f5a8b8552da877af71a331499e3fffcb57b513a.png\" alt=\"Join our Community on Discord!\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Allure Dark Theme GUI</strong> is a part of a bigger project called <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-pack/\">Allure</a>. The pack turns the GUI into a cute shade of obsidian black, making it dark themed while also keeping the original style of <strong>Allure</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/qwxQRGIZ/images/a8d5b5bfada12102ed7a885b2ca5e215c791576c.jpeg\" alt=\"GUI Screenshot\" width=100%></p>  \n<hr>\n<p><br>Please also check out <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-pack/\">Allure</a> if you haven't already, you might enjoy it! If you want to get notified for updates on the pack progress, give me suggestions or you wanna report any bugs, consider joining my Discord server <a href=\"https://discord.gg/C9Q6XFG8T8\">here</a>!</p>\n<br><br><hr>\n<h1>Other Projects!</h1>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-pack\"><img alt=\"Allure 3D Plants\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ab67244910ef4ab4fca79d7e98f4f7afbe9a75ec.webp\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/